quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,"Kananjalo inene Thina Sanika uIbrâhîm ugwebo olulungileyo mandulo, yaye Thina Sasisazi kakhulu ngaye"
  21,52,"Yabona wathi kutata wakhe nakubantu bakubo: “Yeyantoni na le mifanekiso iqingqiweyo nizinikele kangaka kuyo?”"
  21,53,"Bathi bona: “Thina safumana oobawo bethu bekhonza yona.”"
  21,54,"Wathi yena: “Inene nina noobawo benu nanisekulahlekeni okucacileyo.”"
  21,55,"Bathi bona: “Ingaba wena usizele nenyaniso na, okanye ungomnye wabo bagculelayo kusini na?”"
  21,56,"Wathi yena: “Nakanye ukusuka apho, iNkosi yenu yiNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, Eyadala bona, mna ke mayela noko ndingomye wamangqina.”"
  21,57,"Ke kaloku (mna ndifunga) ngoAllâh, ndiya kuqulunqa icebo ngokuchasene nemifanekiso eqingqiweyo yenu nisakuba nimkile nina"
  21,58,"Wayaphula ke (loo mifanekiso iqingqiweyo) yaba ziingceba (yonke) kwashiyeka owona mkhulu kuyo, khona ukuze babuyele kuwo (ngemibuzo)"
  21,59,"Bathi bona: Ngubani owenze le nto koothixo bethu? Inene yena ngomnye wabagabadeli.”"
  21,60,"Bathi: “Sikhe seva enye indodana ithetha ngokuchasene nabo, ebizwa ngokuba nguIbrâhîm.”"
  21,61,"Bathi: “Mziseni phambi kwamehlo wabantu, ukuze babe nobungqina.”"
  21,62,"Bathi: “Ingaba wena ungulo wenze le nto (imbi kangaka) koothixo bethu, hini na wena Ibrâhîm?”"
  21,63,"Wathi yena: “Nakanye, ingasuka nje ibe ngulo umkhulu kunabo owenze loo nto, ngoko ke buzani kubo ukuba (bayakwazi) ukuthetha"
  21,64,"Ke kaloku bajongana bathi omnye komnye: “Inene nina ningabenzi bobubi.”"
  21,65,Baphinda barhoxa (besithi) “Uyayazi nje (nawe) into yokuba ezi (zithixo) azithethi!”
  21,66,"Wathi yena: “Ke ngoku nina niyikhonza (njani) endaweni ka-Allâh into engenaluncedo ingekhe inenze bungozi konke- konke?”"
  21,67,Mkani nina nezo nto nizinqulayo ngaphandle koAllâh! Kanti aninangqondo na?”
  21,68,"Bathi bona: “Mtshiseni nincedise oothixo benu ukuba kukho into ekufuneka niyenzile"
  21,69,"Thina (SinguAllâh) Sathi: “Phola wena mlilo, usindise uIbrâhîm!”"
  21,70,"Ke kaloku babefuna ukumonzakalisa, kodwa Thina Sabenza baba ngabona balahlekelwa kakhulu"
  21,71,Samhlangula ke yena (uIbrâhîm) noLût Sabasa kwilizwe eSalithamsanqelisela indalo yonke
  21,72,Ke kaloku Sampha uIs-hâ’k (uIsake) nomzukulwana uYa’kûb (uYakobi) ngamnye kubo Samenza waba ngcwele
  21,73,"Kananjalo Sabenza iinkokeli, bakhokela (uluntu) ngomyalelo weThu, yaye Satyhila kubo ukwenziwa kwemisebenzi elungileyo, ukumiselwa kweSalâh nokunikelwa kweZakâh yaye babengabanquli beThu"
  21,74,"Ukanti uLût, Samnika ukugweba nolwazi, Samsindisa esixekweni esasisenza izenzo ezingcolileyo. Inene, bona babengabantu bokungcola, bengathobeli konke-konke"
  21,75,"Ke kaloku Samngenisa encebeni yeThu. Inene, yena wayengomnye wamalungisa"